Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:53.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110256,113801}She's an angel! It's like\Nan angel is riding a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:57.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113885,117180}I've never seen\Nsuch a beautiful lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118139,119807}I wish I were that horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120600,122769}I'll be the horse's rear legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123936,125605}Angel?! If she had wings…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125730,127440}…she wouldn't have\Nto ride on the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:09.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127649,129150}They're so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:11.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129233,131736}Rear legs? Is he talking about\Na two-man horse in a play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132487,134781}What about a two-man\Nhorse in a play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135073,136741}It's stupid boy-talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136991,138993}They're talking about\Nthe princess of their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139369,142664}On their way to school\Nthere's a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:26.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142789,146793}In the large yard, a lady\Nwho gracefully rides a horse…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147043,150004}…is the Madonna\Nthat the boys are admiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:33.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150421,153341}They sneak by to watch her\Nevery day on their way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153424,154592}How perverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154926,156427}Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157261,159722}I wonder if Asuka Jr.\Ngoes there, too…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161307,163101}Is she that pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163393,165103}What?! You haven't seen her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165269,166270}– No.\N– Well, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166479,168690}I can take you there today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169482,170858}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171275,172610}I'm not that interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173945,176072}Man! Asuka's head is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:58.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176239,178533}…filled only with\Nthoughts of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:09.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184497,189127}RETURN THE THOROUGHBRED!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204475,205435}You are…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222577,224787}What?! She was cheated\Nand lost the horse…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224912,226247}…that the boys\Nwere talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226664,229625}Yes. The horse's name is Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230626,233838}Both Billy's father and mother\Nwere very famous racehorses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234297,236132}He's a top-notch Thoroughbred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236924,239719}But that Madonna, rather,\NMs. Maki Nishina was against…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239844,241387}…turning him into a racehorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241596,243097}So he became a riding horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248269,250688}That's a very extravagant\Nthing to do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251022,254150}If he's so famous,\Nhe's worth quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254650,256611}Like they say, she must be\Nan extremely rich princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256986,259155}Yes. And according\Nto some people…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259280,262533}…she's wasting a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263493,265828}A man named Soma\Nkept visiting Maki's house…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265912,268790}…asking her to sell Billy to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270249,273211}But Maki flatly refused his offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273419,275880}But Soma wouldn't\Ngive up, and one day…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295525,298027}Well, hello, Lady Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298361,299529}I won't sell Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299654,300738}No matter how many\Ntimes you come here…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:01.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300863,301948}…the answer remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302156,303825}Now, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:08.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304534,308913}I've got a wonderful idea\Nthat may appeal to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:11.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309622,311707}First, please look at this horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314418,315795}He's Wild Bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315878,317630}He's from a very\Nfamous bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:23.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319632,323636}He is as good as your Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:29.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324178,329684}This horse isn't\Na bad trade for Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330059,332687}Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333145,334772}I love Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335189,337650}I'll never give him\Nto someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349328,350288}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351038,352164}What's happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:54.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353958,354917}It's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358045,360423}What are you going to do?\NHis leg is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364927,367972}The medical report\NSoma brought definitely stated…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368431,370266}…that the leg\Nwas broken, Maki said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370766,372143}I've heard that a broken leg is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372476,375521}…the same as\Na death sentence for a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375855,378983}Yes. That's why Soma\Ndemanded Billy in exchange…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:22.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379275,382612}…as if he had\Nthe right to take Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383529,387158}She said her father\Ncouldn't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388075,389702}But something is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390036,392204}Things were\Ntoo convenient for Soma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:35.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392747,395541}Only Soma is winning here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396334,397293}You mean…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397877,400296}Yes. Maki is thinking that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400838,403382}She thinks they were\Nset up from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403925,405885}Soma wanted Billy very badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406510,408846}And the horse's\Nbroken leg was supported…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409221,410765}…only by the medical report.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411474,414352}He tricked them\Nin order to get Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:58.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414936,418105}He had no intention\Nof giving up his horse, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419065,420983}Maki thinks so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:04.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421567,424111}She thinks they\Nsomehow surprised Billy…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424403,426739}…and made him\Nfall into that horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427031,428908}Yes! That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:14.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429784,434080}But Soma has already\Nbecome the legal owner of Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434622,437541}Billy and Maki\Nwill never be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438292,439251}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439335,441921}Under such circumstances,\NSt. Tail can get the horse back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442505,445132}In addition, I'll reveal\NSoma's evil intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446550,448135}But Billy is already scheduled…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:31.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448260,451180}…to go to a ranch\Nin Hokkaido tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452139,453140}And by train!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:34.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453849,454809}Train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:38.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455393,458479}It's the K-Express,\Nleaving Seika Station at 8:02.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458646,460690}We have only four hours\Nuntil its departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:41.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460815,461774}Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473661,475454}What short notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475871,477623}Did he go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477748,479208}How can I send him\Na warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480001,481794}Hey, have you seen Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482461,484046}No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484255,485756}Didn't he go home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486424,487550}Really? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490386,491387}There is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491721,493681}It may be a bit much, but I guess\NI should use that method.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506152,507236}Tonight…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507361,509572}…I'll get Billy\Nfrom the K-Express train…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509697,511532}…leaving Seika Station at 8:02.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513409,514410}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:35.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515036,515995}It's a warning note…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516954,518122}It's elaborate…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518914,520791}Dad! Let me borrow\Nyour train schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520958,522543}The one you always\Nuse for your trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523044,524420}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526297,527256}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527423,528799}Thanks, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529508,533345}But why do you need it, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533971,535431}Well… for something…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539560,540519}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:01.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540644,541604}– Mom!\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541729,543230}Is Meimi going on a trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543439,545024}Not that I know of.\NI haven't heard anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545983,548152}I wonder if she's running away…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:13.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548861,553324}If so, she wouldn't borrow\Nthe schedule from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554742,555701}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556827,559538}There are a lot of things\Ngoing on at her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:23.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561040,563167}It's a difficult age…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568631,571675}Let's see…\Nthe K-Express departs at 8:02…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572259,574261}It will pass that point at…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576514,577473}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577765,580184}SEIKA STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:11.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610798,611841}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612591,615052}St. Tail is coming to steal Billy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615136,616137}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616220,619140}We'll be aboard the train\Nto protect the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619348,620349}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622852,624395}Here comes the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:41.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637616,641036}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646167,647126}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649628,650588}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652840,655134}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:13.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670649,673777}May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:22.70,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:682703,682703}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:27.70,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:687708,687708}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692296,694548}There are no suspicious\Npersons on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695090,696050}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696342,698135}Position yourselves\Nat each place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:41.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699762,701555}No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701805,703265}Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703807,706060}What's the commotion,\NMr. Soma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:50.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707269,710898}Well, this young lady\Nwas doing a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711482,713525}She was trying to open\Nthe door of the livestock car…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713651,715319}…and let Billy escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720616,722660}I beg you! Please return Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723827,725829}You're going too far, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726080,727665}Billy is mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728165,730668}You don't have the right\Nto even touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731210,732169}Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732378,734338}I know you set us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734588,736632}There was no way Billy\Nwould get upset like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:17.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736757,737925}You made him upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738509,740094}He made Billy upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740177,741136}What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741804,743639}Don't say something\Nso stupid without any evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744640,745975}Never come close to this horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747559,748560}Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750145,753023}Who on earth are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754483,755484}Billy…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771500,772543}Billy! Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:55.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774878,775838}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778966,779925}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780050,781010}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781135,782094}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:06.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785764,786724}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:17.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796317,797276}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801822,802823}Billy…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805117,806827}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812249,814918}I see. I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815461,817838}I'm not doing anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:42.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818380,822009}I suppose that girl\Ncan't let go of Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:47.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822593,827097}But St. Tail always has\Na good reason for stealing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:51.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829099,831727}Rather than worrying about that,\Nhow about your security?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832019,834521}Even that girl\Nwas able to get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835689,837066}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837691,839068}We have one officer on each car…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:02.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839610,842780}…and two officers\Nin front of the livestock car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843864,845324}I 'II be at the livestock car, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845616,847701}So it's impossible to break in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848869,849912}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854166,855125}I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873227,874978}First, check the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886990,888242}That must be Soma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888659,890369}I wonder what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:54.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891161,894289}Darn! Why is Billy singled out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894498,896875}St. Tail wants him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897167,899503}That means Billy\Nis a very good horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900212,903340}Of course he is!\NThat's the reason I fell in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904675,906343}He'll bring us a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906760,908512}But that was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909012,911098}You invented\NWild Bunch's broken leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:14.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911265,914435}You blamed it on Billy,\Nand then you got him for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:20.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916186,920399}The key was to use the fact\Nthat the girl didn't want to sell him…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920983,923694}…coupled with your special talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939251,941211}It's like we thought.\NThat's how they did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941920,944423}Now that we know,\NI'll take Billy no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951305,953557}The livestock car\Nis the very last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:56.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953640,956477}Naturally, Asuka Jr. is\Nkeeping it under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:57.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956685,957769}If that's the case…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961732,963817}How's it going?\NIs there anything unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963942,965611}No. Nothing so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:06.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965736,966737}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981460,983587}This is Asuka! I've found St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983670,985881}Everyone! Get up on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989343,990802}Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991553,993347}I was checking it out…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993430,995432}…and there's no officer\Nin the next car or anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995641,997142}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:38.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997434,998685}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998810,1000604}What happened\Nto the kid, Asuka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000771,1002064}I didn't see him, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002189,1003774}Maybe something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005025,1006318}I'm worried about Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006735,1007736}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:48.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007861,1008862}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010239,1012533}Don't move, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013534,1016954}Give up now!\NThere's nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:07.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023877,1027172}Wait a minute.\NIsn't it strange that St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:11.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027339,1031218}…shows up in the front\Nwhen Billy is in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038642,1039726}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:24.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041478,1044064}…Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045315,1047276}…Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058328,1059538}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068213,1070215}Shoot! Someone's on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078140,1079850}Like we thought, it's St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079975,1081768}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083145,1084688}Ignore him! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096533,1098118}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098702,1100746}Get off of me! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100829,1101872}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103957,1105667}Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:28.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106376,1108003}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123310,1124811}St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:55.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134988,1135989}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136448,1137491}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138241,1140911}Three!
